## Phone Number Field

A field that validates phone numbers and provides a suitable editor.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import PhoneNumberField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/phone-number';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field phone = contains(PhoneNumberField);
}
```
